"Spanish Key" 
 
 Recorded Columbia Studio B, New York City August 21, 1969

     Don Alias - Congas
     Juma Santos (credited as "Jim Riley") - Shaker

name: Spanish Key
comments: probably for me the pinnacle of artistic expression
I would like this played at my funeral.
Still hypnotic after all those years.
